data.description: Completely remodeled in 2019 this move in ready home has everything you need on one level. 4 bedrooms plus a large upstairs bonus room. Master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. Attached, oversized 3 stall garage with floor heat. Conveniently located near schools, parks, walking paths and downtown. Call to set up your showing today!
